This is 
-Across The Stars-
Back with the 11-ish am news, I’m a little late today.
There’s a lot to catch up on nowadays.
It’s been a cloudy week and it looks like it’ll be cloudy for a little while longer.

The reports have not been great.. quite the opposite in fact.
If you haven’t heard it already, Trite has suffered its most devastating attack yet.
..The cities have fallen.
I’ll repeat it once more, the cities of Trite have fallen.
According to my sources most of the people were able to flee in time.
I wish I could say I know what will happen next.
But..
I can’t.
What the Triton Military will do next is a mystery.

All I can say is go to the Domes of Demetrica, and survive.

There will be some comforting tunes, please, stay tuned.
And for those still listening, thank you.
